                <h3 class="montserrat">
                    Since our ceremony and reception will both take place in downtown San Francisco, we recommend booking accommodations in SF's Union Square or Financial District.
                </h3>
                <p class="arvo">We recommend the following:</p>
                <p><%= link_to "Palace Hotel", "http://www.sfpalace.com/" %>: 2 New Montgomery Street</p>
                <p><%= link_to "Parc 55", "http://www.parc55hotel.com/" %>: 55 Cyril Magnin Street</p>
                <p><%= link_to "W San Francisco", "http://www.wsanfrancisco.com/" %>: 181 3rd Street</p>
                <p><%= link_to "The Westin St. Francis", "http://westinstfrancis.com/" %>: 335 Powell Street</p>
                <h1 class="small-spacey">Getting Around</h1>
                <h3 class="montserrat">
                    You can arrive to our lunch reception (from the ceremony location) by way of: SF public transportation (Muni), Bay Area public transportation (BART), or private vehicle (e.g., Uber, Lyft, or your own car).
                </h3>
                <p class="arvo">Please use the ingenious tool Google Maps for detailed explanation in case you are confused or get lost.</p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
